{"tid":198833,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人同我一樣，達哥已成為生活嘅一部分","createTime":"2017-04-12T18:42:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-13T11:01:21.000Z","uid":90860,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"96ebe679ca5b097942fa4b5f82bec15662a9bc55","tid":198833,"uid":90860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T18:42:40.000Z","msg":"追左達哥都有成兩三年<br />\n一開始聽潮文覺得幾搞笑，<br />\n晚晚訓唔著都會聽。<br />\n聽哂潮文之後就開始聽佢玩FIFA吹水訓教，<br />\n成日聽佢玩FIFA時講嘅嘢覺得好好笑，<br />\n就開始追台睇埋佢打不同嘅game。<br />\n之前有排達哥因爲backup佬單嘢，<br />\n冇開台成個月我先發現達太祖已經係我生活一部分<br />\n有冇巴打同我一樣係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a567dff7c20132f03e3b9e4081553cd6060a6afc","tid":198833,"uid":1799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T22:54:33.000Z","msg":"一早已經係<br />\n之前back up佬之亂果陣真係生不如死"},{"pid":"6fe9e19080873678461ea262ebcc2a494d12e290","tid":198833,"uid":90860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T02:46:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一早已經係<br />\n之前back up佬之亂果陣真係生不如死</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n嗰時勁驚達哥會不定時開台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好彩冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b055c7063e49fb90cc225543ff7a7b1ef2a9065","tid":198833,"uid":77251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T02:47:51.000Z","msg":"我愛達哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"677aedc2b2f0f5c313555785bdb393ac0d468f03","tid":198833,"uid":86423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T02:48:04.000Z","msg":"冇"},{"pid":"ace12acd170b67bd371ef06acda8b2dc674df66f","tid":198833,"uid":99968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy